{"tid":200071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【魔童回勇】網購每日訂單增2倍，港視股價昨突爆升19%","createTime":"2017-04-13T16:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T04:15:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3f9ecf4f3ccd9f2da92abc4aa25549271b3819","tid":200071,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/HKTV-FB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FHKTV-FB.png&h=6cf7a357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港視主席王維基昨日下午在互聯網經濟論壇上表示，集團旗下網購平台HKTVmall訂單增長相當理想，每日交易量由1,000單大增至3000單，每筆消費由500元升至630元。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，早前在海怡半島開設的實體店銷情理想，生意額達130萬元，更計劃在短期內再下一城，開設8至10間分店，選址將以九龍、港島區為主。至於未來更希望開設300至500間零售店。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTechStart現長期徵稿。歡迎各界Startup人士、科技愛好者來稿交流對時事科技議題的獨特看法。如蒙投稿，請寄 techstart@presslogic.com，另請附上不多於100字個人簡介及近照一張。 文章一經採用將由TechStart編輯部潤飾，更會開設個人專欄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/04/12/article/23971/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2Farticle%2F23971%2F&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=86e92439\" target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/04/12/article/23971/</a>"},{"pid":"c937ca80653f9b328a5f8da1b8c0cfe1855a78bc","tid":200071,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔又成功燈了"},{"pid":"17689d430aaaacb3299158d61d073e0957b98e5b","tid":200071,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"網上店成功左居然搞番實體咁ON居............"},{"pid":"48fb648aa21d993fba58d9fd0c3156dbfed98ea9","tid":200071,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:21:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eb23dc61e45ea4a9b17fb3c95495f3ad898dde4","tid":2000